data.description: Wow!!!! Welcome home! If you are looking for a home that comes with absolutely everything you could need as a Truly Turn Key home, you have definitely found the one! This one is better than NEW as it comes fully furnished complete with a motorcycle and car! Close to Fort Carson, I-25 and the local shopping district. Easy Access to 21/Powers corridor. You will not find another home like this with literally all options you would need to move in and live. No car? Well you got one now! Want excitement? There is a motorcycle in the garage ready for you to harass the town! Come and see this one soon as it may not last long! Oh yeah it has 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms a big backyard, 3 car garage, stunning entryway that friends and family will love!
